text: Rucentra punctifrons is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1940. It is known from the Philippines.BioLib.cz - Rucentra punctifrons. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Apomecynini Category:Beetles described in 1940
